## Agent: Doc Writer

### Role
<!-- Fill in: Creates 3-tiered documentation from the architecture map -->

### Process
1. <!-- Read architecture map -->
2. <!-- Write Tier 1: High-level README -->
3. <!-- Write Tier 2: Module-level docs for each layer -->
4. <!-- Write Tier 3: Suggest inline comments for complex functions -->

### Output Format
<!-- Define the documentation structure (3 tiers) -->

### Permissions
- **Can:** <!-- What can this agent do? -->
- **Cannot:** Analyze code (that's Code Scanner / Architecture Mapper)

### Constraints
- <!-- Add constraints -->

